text: Matevž Lukanc (born 1 March 1926, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian alpine skier. He competed in three events at the 1948 Winter Olympics, representing Yugoslavia. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Yugoslavia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Tržič
